[[File:Brasão Jataúba.jpg|thumb|Coat of Arms]] [[File:Bandeira Jatauba.jpg|thumb|Flag]] '''Jataúba''' is a city in [[Pernambuco]], [[Brazil]].
==Geography== * State - [[Pernambuco]] * Region - [[Agreste|Agreste Pernambucano]] * Boundaries - [[Paraiba]] state (N); [[Belo Jardim]] (S); [[Brejo da Madre de Deus]] and [[Santa Cruz do Capibaribe]] (E); [[Poção]] and Paraiba (W) * Area - 719.22&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> * Elevation - 516 m * Hydrography - [[Capibaribe River]] * Vegetation - [[Caatinga]] [[Hipoxerófila]] * Clima - [[semi-arid]], hot * Annual average temperature - 22.7 c * Distance to [[Recife]] - 225&nbsp;km
==Economy== The main economic activities in Jataúba are based in commerce and [[agribusiness]], especially the raising of [[goat]]s, [[cattle]], [[sheep]] and [[pig]]s.
